7. Final Model Evaluation

The best-performing model was evaluated once on the unseen test dataset.

The following metrics were reported:

Accuracy
Precision
Recall
F1-score
ROC-AUC
PR-AUC

A confusion matrix was generated to examine correct and incorrect predictions.

False positive and false negative cases were analysed to better understand the model's limitations and support future improvements.

