8. Deployment

A Streamlit application was developed to demonstrate the trained model.

The application allows users to enter transaction information, validates the input values, predicts whether a transaction is suspicious, and provides a clear recommendation for fraud analysts.

The application also displays a limitation notice stating that predictions are intended to support human decision-making and should not replace professional judgement.

